//Previous interventions / therapies - Breast amputation


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Mammography/Breast ultrasound
When	I select 'No' radio button
Then 'Add new finding' button is disabled
When	I select 'Yes' radio button
Then 'Previous interventions / therapies' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'Breast augmentation' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled
And Localizer L001 is enabled
When	I select 'R' on the Localizer
Then 'R' part turns red
And 'Autologous fat transfer' radio button in 'R' is enabled
And 'Silicone' radio button is 'R' is enabled
When	I select 'L' on the Localizer
Then 'L' part turns red
And 'Autologous fat transfer' radio button in 'L' is enabled
And 'Silicone' radio button is 'L' is enabled
